item.title: [508] ®×scape secound release
item.dc:creator: @Ashley3 Ashley
item.description:
@Ashley3 wrote:

[quote=“austinsobes, post:199, topic:231493”]Not really good. Not really good at all. Just logging in I noticed that there are so many none working features. For instance, I couldn’t send myself a login message.
p.frames.sendMessage(p, “Welcome back”); causes not just my character to not log in. but it causes the entire server to not work.

Also. Following doesn’t work. trading doesn’t work. Friends doesn’t work. Home teleport didn’t work(This was easily fixed by taking the home teleport out of the case 750 I believe and putting it under the case with the rest of the teleport buttons.)

Next to nothing in this entire server works at all. It’s bare. Running doesn’t even work. Every level starts out at 2, including HP.

Deleting the server. Runs crispy. No lag or anything. But the lack of precoded features is pretty bogus. I’m sure I could fix all of the animations and features myself. But that’s so much work when I could just hit download on another webpage.[/quote]You do realize this server was made in 2008? There are a lot of better ones out there now.

item.dc:creator: @Owner_Bryan Owner_Bryan
item.description:
@Owner_Bryan wrote:

Goodevil:

yes i extracted but it still wont work now none of my 503 508 works whats the love is happening?

I know this is FROM YEARS ago but all you needed too do was Download the orginal Java sun… install restart your computer BOOM! Server would have worked!

What do i do for the IP thing my friend and i are trying to make a server for our school friends but i dnt know what to do for enter ip, can some one please explain to me?

@lightpallyz

Sigh up on [ No-IP.com ] Once your sighed up Click Add Host, Create a host name. Go back too the home page click download No-ip Download the Windows, or Mac, Or linux one whatever kinda computer you have! Once you have it downloaded & installed run it Click select host check the box for the host you made on the website. Make sure you have port forwarded so your host runs on 43593 i have a tutorial on port forwarding just like thousands of other people do too. not hard too find just go to the tutorial section type in port forwarding tutorial. one will pop up… then bam your server is up and running!! people will log in with the IP you created but for you too long in you will have too use the ip [ 127.0.0.0 or 127.0.0.1 ]

ANYWAYS!

OP: I’m so using this!! I don’t care if people think its a crappy out dated server I love it & going to learn off of it so go hate all you want! <3
